{"tid":1352962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王丹看林鄭月娥：當中共走狗很可憐","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:31:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"336aa33a37585c512c61be03862a728e7a3a5333","tid":1352962,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:08:38.000Z","msg":"香港日前發生暴徒痛毆反送中民眾事件，香港特首林鄭月娥卻痛斥民眾，並稱特區政府「與施暴者有關」的說法是「完全沒根據」。對此中國民運人士王丹在臉書痛批「林鄭月娥，已經注定是香港的千古罪人」。<br />\n<br />\n王丹表示，這次港人流血，林鄭月娥一定會付出代價，他稱林鄭月娥已成香港公敵，「下台還是小事，下台後還如何在香港生活？」「下台後恐怕只有遷居他國，低調生活，否則必到處遭人唾罵，一輩子將活在羞辱中，也會連累家人」。<br />\n<br />\n王丹感嘆，當中共的走狗很可憐，出事會被一腳踢開，如果跟的大老出事，還會連同被清算，「想想薄熙來的金主徐明，年紀不大橫死獄中；中共權貴集團大買辦肖建華曾經富可敵國，但直接從香港飯店中被綁走至今生死不知；張陽已經是解放軍上將了，莫名其妙地上吊死在自己家中」。<br />\n<br />\n王丹指出，跟共產黨混，稍有不慎，死無葬身之地，並稱這番話「送給香港罪人林鄭月娥，也送給所有那些跟中共站在一起或者想跟中共站在一起的人，包括台灣的那些人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2860853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2860853&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=9ec9b5e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2860853&h=69245344\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2860853</a>"},{"pid":"33cb2565a45020c2ed59790b8ae9cbfc139dd006","tid":1352962,"uid":48759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:21:45.000Z","msg":"LM睇鄭月娥被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553f8397dc2ba2faf5c92f5a945766e9e92e0c87","tid":1352962,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21522d1b37280df81422642c619e2b88a68e89ae","tid":1352962,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:08:05.000Z","msg":"5毛慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f1ed6254cf0d041a3064c9a6af3a82caca45fc","tid":1352962,"uid":164938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"網上仲有好多人唔知係27定28號<br />\n係改左做27號光復 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEBdKMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEBdKMw.png&h=d464cba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoFYVTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoFYVTc.png&h=b80a306d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74373b45872c8f9254c2e95295f0fc0c51aafc1e","tid":1352962,"uid":12335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2e297ed81ce659ca4b71c653f480453929bf088","tid":1352962,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"無官方是一身輕，伴君伴虎自古云。歸家便是三生幸，鳥盡弓藏走狗烹。&hellip;&hellip;君王下旨拿功臣，劍擁兵圍，繩纏索綁，肉顫心驚。恨不能，得便處投河跳井。悔不及，起初時詐死埋名。《碧血劍》<br />\n<br />\n昔日功臣都難免，何況你林鄭係落哂習敗北面既廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c50801d6ddf0bf6b081665d6a3e83c7def5921f","tid":1352962,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}